              <h3>Skills Development</h3>
              <p>Students can improve their technical skills, soft skills, and gain hands-on experience by participating in coding projects, hackathons, workshops, and other activities organized by the club. </p>
            </div>
            <div >
              <h3>Co-op, Internship, and Career Exploration</h3>
              <p> Our Executive and Founding members have co-op and internship experiences within various tech fields. Through IDEA Chats, workshops, and talks by industry professionals, students can gain insights into various co-ops, internships, and career paths within software engineering which can help them make informed decisions about their future career goals. 
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
